high_descs: Walk to the microwave to your right.
Grab the egg inside the microwave.
Turn left and walk to the fridge to your left.
Place the egg inside the fridge, chill it and then remove it from the fridge.
Turn right, walk straight, make a quick right and walk to the microwave to your left.
Place the cool egg into the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place a cool egg in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn right and go to the microwave
Grab the egg out of the microwave
Turn left and stop at the fridge
Put the egg in the fridge and close the door. Then take the egg out
Turn around and go to the microwave
Put the egg in the microwave
anns.task_desc: Putting a cold egg in the microwave

high_descs: Move to your right until you're in front of the microwave.
Get the egg from inside the microwave then close the door.
Turn left and walk to the stove then move to your left until you're in front of the fridge then take a step forward.
Chill the egg in the fridge then get it back out and close the door.
Please head back to the microwave.
Put the egg back in the microwave then close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold egg in the microwave.
